Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.16,0:00:12.96,Default,,0,0,0,,First lesson of the day. We\Nvery carefully set the table
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.00,0:00:15.70,Default,,0,0,0,,without using magic\Nso that-- YIPES!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.24,0:00:22.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you-- how-- when-- what?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.78,0:00:23.44,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.04,0:00:27.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I said no magic. You were\Nsupposed to do it by hoof
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.22,0:00:29.08,Default,,0,0,0,,so I could work in\Na friendship lesson.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.46,0:00:32.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh. I heard set the table\Nand just kinda went for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.54,0:00:35.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, if you\Nhadn't used magic,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.82,0:00:37.70,Default,,0,0,0,,you'd have heard\Nme say, uh,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.36,0:00:41.60,Default,,0,0,0,,this plate represents your\Nhead, this spoon is your heart
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.78,0:00:46.14,Default,,0,0,0,,and the knives... are sharp.\NAlways be careful with knives.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.08,0:00:50.02,Default,,0,0,0,,The metaphors make more\Nsense when you're actually
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.14,0:00:51.52,Default,,0,0,0,,setting the table.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.04,0:00:53.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Should I change it back?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.12,0:00:56.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I just want to make sure\Nyou're ready for this dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.48,0:00:58.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Princess Celestia will be\Njoining us tomorrow night
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.62,0:01:00.36,Default,,0,0,0,,to see how the friendship\Nlessons are going.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.32,0:01:03.90,Default,,0,0,0,,If it's just you, me\Nand Princess Celestia,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.94,0:01:05.53,Default,,0,0,0,,why are there\Nfour seats?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.88,0:01:08.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, the whole point is for\Nyou to bring a new friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.76,0:01:10.52,Default,,0,0,0,,That way the Princess\Nwill see for herself
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.56,0:01:11.67,Default,,0,0,0,,just how far\Nyou've come.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.98,0:01:14.24,Default,,0,0,0,,And how good a\Nteacher you have.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.96,0:01:16.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't choose. I\Nlike all your friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.18,0:01:20.18,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the best part. You\Nhave to make a new friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.48,0:01:22.90,Default,,0,0,0,,New friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.78,0:01:26.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, maybe I'll just\Nforce friendships
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.32,0:01:29.04,Default,,0,0,0,,by magically enslaving\Nthe entire population
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.08,0:01:30.25,Default,,0,0,0,,of Ponyville!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.74,0:01:32.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Starlight!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.54,0:01:34.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Kidding! Heh heh heh.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.56,0:01:53.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Regular subtitles\Nby YayPonies\NWe have muffins!\Nhttps://yp1.yayponies.no/
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.20,0:02:17.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see. Make new\Nfriends in Ponyville,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.15,0:02:19.40,Default,,0,0,0,,the friendliest\Nplace in Equestria.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.78,0:02:21.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Shouldn't be hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.35,0:02:22.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Need to make a new\Nfriend, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.78,0:02:24.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I know just the\Npony for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.73,0:02:27.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Ms. Starlight\NGlimmer,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.08,0:02:28.16,Default,,0,0,0,,meet Mrs. Cake.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.03,0:02:33.46,Default,,0,0,0,,How are you, dearie?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.95,0:02:35.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you baking?\NCan I help?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.88,0:02:46.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow. Mrs. Cake! Look what\Nyour "new friend" made you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.83,0:02:50.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah ha ha! New friend? I like\Nthe sound of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.20,0:02:51.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Howza-whoza!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.13,0:02:53.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you trying to put\Nme out of business
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.73,0:02:56.06,Default,,0,0,0,,with your fancy\Nmagica-thingy-whatsit cake?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.40,0:02:59.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.70,0:03:01.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.90,0:03:07.93,Default,,0,0,0,,In her defense,\Nit is delicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.00,0:03:14.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I think I have just the\Npony for you, Starlight.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.18,0:03:16.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Meet Big Mac.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.50,0:03:18.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Eyup.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.78,0:03:21.16,Default,,0,0,0,,He's not much\Nof a talker.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.03,0:03:23.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.78,0:03:26.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh that's too bad. I\Nlove a good conversation.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.93,0:03:38.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Eyyyyyyyyup-yup-yeah-yeah-you\Ndid something!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.35,0:03:40.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa! What's happening?\NI feel really weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.93,0:03:43.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm talking so much\Nand I'm so articulate
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.08,0:03:45.23,Default,,0,0,0,,enunciating with such\Nprecise pronunciation!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.30,0:03:49.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Annie Apple Awoke\NAnd Accidentally Ate
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.25,0:03:54.50,Default,,0,0,0,,an Auburn Azalea!\NAaaah! MAKE IT STOP!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.08,0:03:59.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't be friends with\Nsomepony who doesn't talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.55,0:04:04.45,Default,,0,0,0,,And I guess my first\Ninstinct shouldn't be to
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.50,0:04:06.88,Default,,0,0,0,,magically command ponies to\Nact the way I want them to.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.65,0:04:10.58,Default,,0,0,0,,All right! I'll\Nchange him back!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.95,0:04:14.28,Default,,0,0,0,,The trick to\Nfinding a new friend
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.40,0:04:16.45,Default,,0,0,0,,is to render\Nyourself radiant.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.75,0:04:18.95,Default,,0,0,0,,First impressions count\Na great deal, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.38,0:04:22.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm glad you all got\Npast my first impression.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.53,0:04:25.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, everypony deserves\Na second chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.68,0:04:29.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh now, I have a\Ntop-notch idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.20,0:04:31.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm thinking pastel\Nsilk here and here,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.18,0:04:33.88,Default,,0,0,0,,with crinoline underneath.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.15,0:04:36.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You really think a new outfit\Nwill help me meet ponies?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.83,0:04:40.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, with the right outfit,\Nyou can do anything, darling.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.00,0:04:41.90,Default,,0,0,0,,When will it be ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.13,0:04:42.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Three weeks.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.73,0:04:45.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Dinner's tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.65,0:04:48.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, then! How about\Na hat from the, ahem,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.58,0:04:49.58,Default,,0,0,0,,"clearance bin?"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.40,0:04:57.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe not.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.33,0:05:01.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Nopony's gonna make\Nfriends with you
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.43,0:05:03.26,Default,,0,0,0,,because of your outfit.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.38,0:05:07.71,Default,,0,0,0,,The only thing you want a new\Nfriend draped in is coolness.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.88,0:05:08.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Like you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.83,0:05:11.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, but you already\Nknow me, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.03,0:05:13.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Spitfire!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.98,0:05:15.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.85,0:05:16.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.45,0:05:20.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Only the Wonderboltiest\NPony in the Wonderbolts.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.38,0:05:21.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, I'll\Nintroduce you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.85,0:05:27.55,Default,,0,0,0,,You coming or what?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.08,0:05:30.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess my first\Nquestion would be...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.68,0:05:32.31,Default,,0,0,0,,what's a Wonderbolt?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.55,0:05:36.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You've never heard\Nof the Wonderbolts?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.48,0:05:37.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Where have you been?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.48,0:05:41.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Heh... enslaving\Nvillages, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.88,0:05:43.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.33,0:05:50.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You're adorable, but probably\Nnot what Twilight had in mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.83,0:06:00.73,Default,,0,0,0,,What is going on?\NThis is Ponyville!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.23,0:06:02.63,Default,,0,0,0,,If I can't make\Na friend here,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.63,0:06:04.63,Default,,0,0,0,,there's got to be\Nsomething wrong with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.28,0:06:08.03,Default,,0,0,0,,OK. Calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.23,0:06:10.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Nobody makes friends\Nwith a total stress case.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.28,0:06:18.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop stressing!\NSTOP STRESSING!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.33,0:06:38.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Ahhh. This is just\Nwhat I needed.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.40,0:06:40.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell me about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.18,0:06:43.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You ever have one\Nof those days?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.45,0:06:45.75,Default,,0,0,0,,For me, they're all\None of those days.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.88,0:06:46.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha-ha-ha.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.08,0:06:50.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to start coming here\Nevery time I visit Ponyville.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.02,0:06:54.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not from here either. I've\Nbeen trying to make friends,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.13,0:06:56.88,Default,,0,0,0,,but it's not easy.\NThey're not saying it,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.05,0:06:59.45,Default,,0,0,0,,but I think everypony\Nknows about my past.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.85,0:07:02.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I... may have been\Na tiny bit...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.40,0:07:05.28,Default,,0,0,0,,...completely and\Nutterly evil?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.70,0:07:07.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Ponies judge me on\Nmy past, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.43,0:07:12.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Finally, a pony I\Ncan relate to.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.60,0:07:16.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Soup spoon, salad fork, pasta\Nspoon, strawberry pick.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.33,0:07:19.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm beginning to think\Nthat after Friendship,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.30,0:07:20.88,Default,,0,0,0,,the greatest magic\Nof all...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.93,0:07:23.78,Default,,0,0,0,,is proper silverware\Nplacement.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.13,0:07:26.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Twilight, guess what!\NI made a new friend!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.00,0:07:28.75,Default,,0,0,0,,That's fantastic news.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.03,0:07:30.01,Default,,0,0,0,,She's great!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.10,0:07:30.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Great!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.98,0:07:31.98,Default,,0,0,0,,She's powerful!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.18,0:07:33.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Powerful?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.20,0:07:33.68,Default,,0,0,0,,She's--
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.80,0:07:36.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} Hello, Princess.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.50,0:07:39.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Trixie?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.33,0:07:45.51,Default,,0,0,0,,You know each other?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.98,0:07:47.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You could say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.50,0:07:49.65,Default,,0,0,0,,We've had our\Ndifferences.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.90,0:07:52.98,Default,,0,0,0,,What matters is Twilight\Ngave me a second chance
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.05,0:07:54.78,Default,,0,0,0,,and I appreciate it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.78,0:08:02.62,Default,,0,0,0,,So, um, what brings\Nyou to Ponyville?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.65,0:08:07.23,Default,,0,0,0,,The great and powerful\NTrixie has come to perform
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.23,0:08:12.26,Default,,0,0,0,,a new stage show of grand\Nillusion. I'm calling it
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.43,0:08:15.63,Default,,0,0,0,,"The Humble and\NPenitent Trixie's
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.70,0:08:17.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Equestrian Apology Tour."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.48,0:08:19.64,Default,,0,0,0,,That's kind of\Na mouthful.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.80,0:08:20.80,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a working title.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.38,0:08:24.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Starlight? A moment?\NOver here?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.73,0:08:30.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I know I said make\Nfriends with "anypony,"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.10,0:08:33.15,Default,,0,0,0,,but... well, with Trixie's\Npast and your past,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.43,0:08:36.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not so sure she's\Nthe best "first friend."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.59,0:08:43.03,Default,,0,0,0,,But whatever she did,\Nyou've forgiven her, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.38,0:08:44.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.58,0:08:45.56,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.88,0:08:47.73,Default,,0,0,0,,She wasn't the\Nnicest pony.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.38,0:08:52.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you did say anypony\Nand I just assumed
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.18,0:08:54.23,Default,,0,0,0,,that you'd trust me\Nto make my own friends
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.28,0:08:56.71,Default,,0,0,0,,the way Princess\NCelestia trusted you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.20,0:09:00.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You're\Nright. I trust you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.58,0:09:02.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Just be back in\Ntime for the dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.30,0:09:04.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks, Twilight.\NYou won't regret it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.55,0:09:08.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope not.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.28,0:09:12.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Ugh.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.18,0:09:16.73,Default,,0,0,0,,This Magic Show's gonna\Nbe the greatest thing
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.75,0:09:18.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Ponyville's ever seen.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.48,0:09:30.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Everypony always says they'll\Ngive you a second chance,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.00,0:09:33.70,Default,,0,0,0,,but deep down,\Nthey never forget.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.53,0:09:36.08,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what I'm\Nworried about.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.38,0:09:38.16,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.58,0:09:42.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard what Twilight said\Nabout me and she's right;
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.00,0:09:44.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I wasn't very nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.93,0:09:47.88,Default,,0,0,0,,So, I'd understand if you\Ndidn't want to be friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.30,0:09:50.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you kidding?\NYou're the first pony
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.75,0:09:53.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I've met who has\Nany idea how I feel.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.43,0:09:58.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you keep a secret?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.95,0:10:00.90,Default,,0,0,0,,What are friends for?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.98,0:10:03.11,Default,,0,0,0,,The things I've done,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.40,0:10:06.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I did them because I\Nwas jealous of Twilight.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.20,0:10:08.03,Default,,0,0,0,,She's just the\Nbest at everything
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.23,0:10:10.71,Default,,0,0,0,,and I wanted to beat\Nher at something.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.35,0:10:12.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Your secret's\Nsafe with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.05,0:10:14.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.53,0:10:15.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Wanna help me\Nunpack my wagon?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.20,0:10:20.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I spend a lot of time on\Nthe road with my wagon,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.88,0:10:23.58,Default,,0,0,0,,so it might be\Na tad messy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.03,0:10:27.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe I can help. I'm pretty\Ngood at organizing stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.05,0:10:30.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Magic props,\Nbrainwashed crowds.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.53,0:10:37.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Psssst! Psssst! Psssst!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.55,0:10:39.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Shhhhh!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.15,0:10:44.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, I'll catch up. I think\Nthere's something in my hoof.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.50,0:10:46.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure, the wagon's right\Naround the corner.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.50,0:10:51.28,Default,,0,0,0,,So. How's it going\Nwith your new friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.65,0:10:54.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Great. Thanks for asking in\Na completely not creepy way.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.89,0:10:57.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Because, you know, if it isn't\Nworking out for any reason,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.80,0:10:59.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I could introduce you\Nto my friend, here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.23,0:11:02.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.83,0:11:05.06,Default,,0,0,0,,No, no. You can\Ncome out now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.28,0:11:08.61,Default,,0,0,0,,You like music, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.80,0:11:11.30,Default,,0,0,0,,DJ-Pon3'd be the perfect\Nfriend for tonight's
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.38,0:11:14.11,Default,,0,0,0,,incredibly important\Ndinner with Celestia.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.63,0:11:17.53,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, if you decide to\Nmake a last minute change.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.93,0:11:21.48,Default,,0,0,0,,So... back at your castle\Nwhen you said, "I trust you,"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.55,0:11:23.73,Default,,0,0,0,,you meant, "I\Ndon't trust you."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.33,0:11:28.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Who can really say who said\Nwhat? I know I can't. Can you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.60,0:11:33.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Starlight, I'm just trying\Nto look out for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.92,0:11:37.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I appreciate it, but\Nyou're wrong about Trixie.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.28,0:11:40.03,Default,,0,0,0,,She's just like me. We\Nhave a real connection.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.50,0:11:44.80,Default,,0,0,0,,That's kind of what I'm afraid\Nof. OH! What about her!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.18,0:11:49.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, Twilight! I know\Nyou're trying to help,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.13,0:11:52.75,Default,,0,0,0,,but I need to make\Nfriends on my own
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.75,0:11:54.63,Default,,0,0,0,,if I'm going to\Nbecome a better pony.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.95,0:11:56.83,Default,,0,0,0,,But do you really\Nthink Trixie is the one
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.83,0:11:57.98,Default,,0,0,0,,to help you with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.48,0:12:00.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, Trixie was right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.68,0:12:02.93,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not really giving\Nher a second chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.20,0:12:06.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder what that says\Nabout how you feel about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.03,0:12:13.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! Now he'd be PERFECT!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.90,0:12:14.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Ugh.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.53,0:12:21.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I was thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.95,0:12:24.48,Default,,0,0,0,,You said Twilight is better\Nthan you at everything,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.70,0:12:27.53,Default,,0,0,0,,but that's not true.\NYou're better at magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.83,0:12:30.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Only when I'm wearing a\Nsoul-sucking evil amulet,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.30,0:12:31.93,Default,,0,0,0,,so I don't think\Nthat counts.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.70,0:12:34.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Funny story. Don't\Nneed to get into it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.80,0:12:36.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I meant stage magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.73,0:12:42.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, of course. Great?\NYes. Powerful? Obviously.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.48,0:12:44.68,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'm not the best.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.98,0:12:47.37,Default,,0,0,0,,As great and powerful\Nas I am,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.55,0:12:51.03,Default,,0,0,0,,there's one trick I've\Nnever been able to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.55,0:12:54.50,Default,,0,0,0,,The Moon-shot\NManticore Mouth Dive.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.15,0:12:58.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Only one magician has\Never pulled it off:
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.18,0:13:01.66,Default,,0,0,0,,my hero, Hoofdini.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.45,0:13:05.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You are supposed to blast\Nyourself into the open mouth
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.48,0:13:07.38,Default,,0,0,0,,of a hungry Manticore.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.30,0:13:11.00,Default,,0,0,0,,After the Manticore chews\Nyou up and swallows you,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.05,0:13:13.18,Default,,0,0,0,,you magically step\Nout of a box
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.20,0:13:15.10,Default,,0,0,0,,on the other side\Nof the stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.85,0:13:19.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Completely unharmed.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.90,0:13:21.50,Default,,0,0,0,,That sounds very...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.58,0:13:22.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Dangerous?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.55,0:13:24.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I was going to\Nsay, "cool."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.80,0:13:26.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew I liked you\Nfor a reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.85,0:13:30.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know how he did it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.93,0:13:33.78,Default,,0,0,0,,If I tried it, I'd get\Nchewed up and swallowed
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.80,0:13:34.83,Default,,0,0,0,,by that Manticore.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.33,0:13:37.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Not if you could\Nuse real magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.85,0:13:40.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Obviously. Way\Nto rub it in.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.98,0:13:44.58,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I mean I could help.\NYou could start the trick
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.80,0:13:46.08,Default,,0,0,0,,and right before\Nyou got chewed up,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.35,0:13:47.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I could use magic\Nto save you
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.75,0:13:51.09,Default,,0,0,0,,and make you appear\Nin the black box.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.20,0:13:53.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess that would work.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.85,0:13:57.90,Default,,0,0,0,,But if you made one\Nmistake, I'd be a goner.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.78,0:14:02.05,Default,,0,0,0,,When it comes to magic,\NI don't make mistakes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.23,0:14:05.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe I could be your...\N"magic-show-helper-pony?"
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.80,0:14:09.41,Default,,0,0,0,,We call it "assistant" in\Nthe magician biz and...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.63,0:14:12.33,Default,,0,0,0,,nopony's ever offered\Nto help before.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.50,0:14:14.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I'd be honored.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.85,0:14:18.33,Default,,0,0,0,,You may have just made my\Ngreat and powerful magic show
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.35,0:14:21.50,Default,,0,0,0,,even better, which I\Ndidn't think was possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.40,0:14:24.83,Default,,0,0,0,,We're gonna blow\Nthem away tonight!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.83,0:14:28.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I can't. Tonight's this
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.68,0:14:31.34,Default,,0,0,0,,"incredibly important"\Ndinner with Twilight.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.80,0:14:32.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.70,0:14:35.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I vent for a minute?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.10,0:14:37.44,Default,,0,0,0,,What are friends for?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.63,0:14:40.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Even after Twilight\Nsays she trusts me,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.08,0:14:41.98,Default,,0,0,0,,she clearly doesn't\Ntrust me enough
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.03,0:14:43.78,Default,,0,0,0,,to choose my own friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.25,0:14:47.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess you were right.\NNo second chances.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.23,0:14:51.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I wish I could say\NI was surprised.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.00,0:14:55.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, lucky for\N"Princess" Twilight
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.88,0:14:58.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I have my magic\Nshow tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.65,0:15:01.08,Default,,0,0,0,,If you have to go\Nto the dinner,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.16,0:15:03.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I completely understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.68,0:15:06.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I just hope I find\Na way to survive
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.48,0:15:11.15,Default,,0,0,0,,the Moon-Shot Manticore Mouth\NDive without my new assistant.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.78,0:15:26.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Starlight Glimmer should\Nbe here any minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.68,0:15:30.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Any... minute...\Nnow.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.83,0:15:34.16,Default,,0,0,0,,How about I\Nintroduce everyone?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.63,0:15:38.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Our friendship lessons\Nare going so well.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.33,0:15:40.41,Default,,0,0,0,,She made three\Nnew friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.93,0:15:43.96,Default,,0,0,0,,She has such great\Ntaste in friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.23,0:15:46.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know where she\Nwould have learned that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.28,0:15:50.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Starlight Glimmer? I thought\Nyou said nose-hair trimmers!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.00,0:15:54.98,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on? I'm hungry!\NAnd my nose is too hairy!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.65,0:16:00.39,Default,,0,0,0,,HAHA! Cranky Doodle,\Nyou're so funny!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.68,0:16:03.11,Default,,0,0,0,,If you'll excuse me, I'm\Ngoing to check the kitchen.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.45,0:16:07.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe she got lost amongst\Nthe... artichokes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.93,0:16:13.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Starlight? Has anyone\Nseen Starlight Glimmer?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.70,0:16:15.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm looking for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.45,0:16:19.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Trixie!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.93,0:16:23.61,Default,,0,0,0,,So this is the "The Humble\Nand Penitent Trixie's
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.65,0:16:25.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Equestrian Apology Tour."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.40,0:16:27.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Ain't that a\Nmouthful of molasses.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.35,0:16:29.55,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a working title.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.93,0:16:33.21,Default,,0,0,0,,This is going to be the\Ngreatest night of my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.73,0:16:36.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me, our lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.28,0:16:39.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so glad that we're\Nnot at that boring dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.50,0:16:40.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Ahem.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.48,0:16:44.58,Default,,0,0,0,,You just decided to skip our\Ndinner without telling me?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.85,0:16:46.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you aware that\Nat this very moment,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.98,0:16:49.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Princess Celestia is\Nwaiting for you at a table--
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.98,0:16:52.28,Default,,0,0,0,,--with exquisite\Nsilverware placement?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.55,0:16:53.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.68,0:16:55.28,Default,,0,0,0,,This is exactly why
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.30,0:16:56.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't want you to make\Nfriends with Trixie.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.18,0:17:00.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah-HA! You still\Ndon't trust me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.73,0:17:02.73,Default,,0,0,0,,But guess what, "princess?"
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.83,0:17:05.36,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't matter if you want\Nto give me a second chance
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.40,0:17:09.66,Default,,0,0,0,,or not. Starlight had to\Nchoose between you and me
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.98,0:17:16.27,Default,,0,0,0,,and she chose me! Your pupil\Nchose me! So HA. I win!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.10,0:17:21.30,Default,,0,0,0,,You win? That sounds like you\Njust made friends with me
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.43,0:17:22.51,Default,,0,0,0,,to beat Twilight.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.75,0:17:24.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Exactly!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.60,0:17:30.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait. I mean, no! I got caught\Nup in the moment. I like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.85,0:17:32.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Beating Twilight\Nis just a bonus.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.65,0:17:34.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, saying that\Ndidn't help, did it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.05,0:17:39.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I should have known.\NNopony else in Ponyville
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.05,0:17:41.65,Default,,0,0,0,,wanted to be my\Nfriend. Why would you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.73,0:17:46.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait! It's not like\Nthat! I am your friend!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.38,0:17:48.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.00,0:17:52.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you "won." I\Nhope you're happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.33,0:17:56.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like the great\Nand powerful Trixie
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.50,0:17:58.75,Default,,0,0,0,,is back to a solo show...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.05,0:18:00.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Trixie?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.58,0:18:05.42,Default,,0,0,0,,...which is exactly\Nthe way she likes it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.78,0:18:08.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you,\NPrincess Twilight,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.10,0:18:10.08,Default,,0,0,0,,for getting rid of\Nthat annoying pony
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.13,0:18:14.31,Default,,0,0,0,,who wanted to be my first\Nfriend. I am not sad at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.80,0:18:17.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I definitely don't feel\Nlike my heart is breaking
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.40,0:18:18.85,Default,,0,0,0,,into a million pieces.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.15,0:18:27.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Come one, come all!\NCome and see
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.48,0:18:31.13,Default,,0,0,0,,"The Pathetic and Friendless\NTrixie's Way-To-Go-Dumb-Dumb
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.15,0:18:34.84,Default,,0,0,0,,You-Really-Messed-It-Up-This-\NTime Repentance Tour."
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.33,0:18:39.23,Default,,0,0,0,,IT'S A WORKING TITLE!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.05,0:18:43.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Behold, your fears come true...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.13,0:18:45.13,Default,,0,0,0,,a pony-eating MANTICORE,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.48,0:18:51.23,Default,,0,0,0,,for tonight, the great\Nand powerful Trixie
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.23,0:18:55.31,Default,,0,0,0,,will be performing the\NMoon-shot Manticore Mouth Dive.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.00,0:19:01.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, now. Save your gasps\Nfor when I defy the beast's
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.53,0:19:05.88,Default,,0,0,0,,jaws of doom and appear\Ninside that black box.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.40,0:19:08.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I was supposed to\Nperform this trick
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.48,0:19:10.98,Default,,0,0,0,,with my great and\Npowerful assistant,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.30,0:19:14.25,Default,,0,0,0,,who was also my great\Nand powerful friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.88,0:19:21.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Starlight? When I first\Ncame to Ponyville,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.70,0:19:24.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Princess Celestia gave me\Nroom to make my own decisions
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.98,0:19:28.17,Default,,0,0,0,,and my own friends. I need to\Ngive you the same freedom.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.48,0:19:29.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I shouldn't have tried
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.28,0:19:30.76,Default,,0,0,0,,to pick and choose\Nyour friends for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.23,0:19:36.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Just like me, you have to\Nmake your own decisions...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.20,0:19:38.53,Default,,0,0,0,,and your own friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.95,0:19:43.88,Default,,0,0,0,,But, what if Trixie really was\Nusing me just to one up you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.25,0:19:46.73,Default,,0,0,0,,From what I've seen...\Nshe's the real thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.85,0:19:53.75,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's not my place to\Njudge. It's all up to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.43,0:20:01.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Starlight? If\Nyou're out there
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.33,0:20:02.98,Default,,0,0,0,,and you still want\Nto be friends,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.43,0:20:06.41,Default,,0,0,0,,let's be great and\Npowerful together.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.08,0:20:07.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.58,0:20:15.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Ahhhhh!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.02,0:20:31.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Behold, the pate and\Ngrowerful Triskee!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.60,0:20:46.93,Default,,0,0,0,,And now, I'm proud\Nto introduce
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.00,0:20:49.75,Default,,0,0,0,,my great and powerful\Nassistant...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.12,0:20:54.43,Default,,0,0,0,,and best friend...\NStarlight Glimmer!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.28,0:21:00.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Trixie!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.40,0:21:01.68,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.95,0:21:04.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I was wrong,\NI'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.63,0:21:05.97,Default,,0,0,0,,And I have to hand\Nit to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.10,0:21:08.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I could never have pulled\Noff a trick like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.93,0:21:13.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you... Princess.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.63,0:21:30.56,Default,,0,0,0,,How do you get yer hair\Nto do that all the time?
